ight weeks a successful beginning by any measure also the pimco enhanced short maturity strategy fund nysearcamint a moneymarketlike etf has  billion in assets making it the biggest active etf to date the wisdomtree emerging markets local debt fund nysearcaeld comes in a close second with  billion in assets interest in inflationprotected bonds has been on the upswing amid growing concern among investors that excessive monetary stimulus from central banks such as the federal reserve is creating inflationary pressure that will rear its head before long the ishares barclays tips bond nysearcatip the biggest fixedincome etf and the eighthbiggest us etf at the end of march had  billion in assets as of april  according to data compiled by indexuniversecom the effective duration of the planned etf will normally vary within plus or minus two years of the effective duration of the pimco global advantage inflationlinked bond index duration is a measure used to determine the sensitivity of a securitys price to changes in interest rates the longer a securitys duration the more sensitive it will be to changes in interest rates the filing said the value of the bonds principal or the interest income paid is adjusted to track changes in an official inflation measure permalink  copy copyright  indexuniverse llc all rights reserved dont forget to check indexuniversecoms etf data section copyright ®  indexuniverse llc  all rights reserved the views and opinions expressed herein are the views and opinions of the author and do not necessarily reflect those of nasdaq inc this article appears in investing  etfs referenced symbols eld  mint  tip more from indexuniverse subscribe powershares launches local em bond etf powershares to launch local em bond etf emerging global plans first bond etfs related etfs articles subscribe europe etfs are turning a lot of heads   pm first uslisted bond etfs celebrate year milestone   pm etf strategies to help position for the rest of the year   pm contri